4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer." This course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge and aims to kickstart their career as a data scientist. The course duration is 16 weeks, with three classes per week. The class size is limited to a maximum of 12 people. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker (Google Data Studio), Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. They will also gain experience in supervised and unsupervised learning models. The course emphasizes practical problem-solving and provides hands-on experience in tackling real-life cases. Students will also learn to strategize and develop their own AI projects, from development to deployment and maintenance, with a focus on privacy and security. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit their website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop